Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar usuário
PUT {{baseURL}}/protected/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nome Atualizado",
  "email": "email@atualizado.com",
  "phone": "54988888888",
  "password": "senha2"
}

### deletar usuário
