Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar pets
GET {{baseURL}}/protected/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get pet by ID
GET {{baseURL}}/protected/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar pet
POST {{baseURL}}/protected/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bolt",
  "age": 2,
  "species": "Cachorro",
  "size": "medium",
  "status": "available",
  "description": "Muito dócil"
}

### Atualizar pet
PUT {{baseURL}}/protected/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Faree",
  "age": 2,
  "species": "Cachorro",
  "size": "medium",
  "status": "adopted",
  "description": "Muito dócil"
}

### Delete pet
DELETE {{baseURL}}/protected/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

